Problem 1
Write a program to calculate the size of integer type data.

Run
#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
	int size_of_int=sizeof(int);
	printf("The size of int data type = %d\n",size_of_int );
return 0;
}
Output:
The size of int data type = 4
